HEADWORD: Denutrition
<hw>De`nu*tri"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>The opposition of nutrition; the failure of
nutrition causing the breaking down of tissue.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

